HEADWORD: Unmerchantable
<hw>Un*mer"chant*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Com.)</fld> <def>Not merchantable; not fit for market; being of a
kind, quality, or quantity that is unsalable.</def>
